Class CacheNode

java.lang.Object
  com.amazonaws.services.elasticache.model.CacheNode

public class CacheNode
extends Object

A Cache Cluster is made up of one or more Cache Nodes. Each Cache Node is an separate endpoint servicing the memcached protocol.
